<subSubSection id="F7D86578FFB41B03FDD3FCD7015945C3" pageId="10" pageNumber="160" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="BF7D36F3FFB41B03FDD3FCD7015945C3" blockId="10.[458,1854,662,1013]" pageId="10" pageNumber="160">
This tropical American ladybeetle was probably introduced into 
<collectingCountry id="C7D57663FFB41B03F9A8FCD701DC45B8" box="[1650,1754,866,910]" name="Guam" pageId="10" pageNumber="160">Guam</collectingCountry>
